long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you search profitable items with stickers from Counter-Strike (CS:GO & CS2) on the CsMoney Market. This makes trading easy and convenient!

The extension analyzes the latest items that users have posted on the CsMoney Market, analyzes their price and compares them with your price and calculates the overpayment for stickers and in case of a favorable price of the item, sends you a notification!
